snippet.title: Astera - Co-Operative Multiplayer Gameplay (Alpha)
snippet.description:
Alpha gameplay of a dungeon run featuring the ranger from our upcoming ARPG, Astera.

Step into Astera, a steampunk-infused fantasy world. Play your way in this fast-paced Action RPG featuring dual class specialization, rogue-like dungeons, a vast open world to explore and co-operative multiplayer. Crafted with passion by a dedicated team of action RPG enthusiasts.

Wishlist Astera on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2866330/Astera/
Join our Discord community: https://discord.gg/UGvbBZgDc2
